=Fight On, Move Toward the Goal=

69
00:05:23,580 --> 00:05:24,820
Today's significance

70
00:05:24,820 --> 00:05:25,860
is clear to everyone.

71
00:05:26,060 --> 00:05:27,380
Time to separate the wheat

72
00:05:27,660 --> 00:05:28,940
from the chaff.

73
00:05:29,980 --> 00:05:31,180
I'll say it again.

74
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:33,500
Show your best skills.

75
00:05:33,740 --> 00:05:35,340
Pass the test,

76
00:05:35,820 --> 00:05:36,780
and you race.

77
00:05:36,780 --> 00:05:37,820
Fail?

78
00:05:38,180 --> 00:05:40,140
Pack up and go home.

79
